San_Jose.Our Lady of La Vang Parish: Our Lady of La Vang Parish (Vietnamese: Giáo Xứ Đức Mẹ La Vang), formerly Saint Patrick Proto-Cathedral Parish, is a national parish of the Roman Catholic Diocese of San Jose in California serving the Vietnamese community. The proto-cathedral is located in Downtown San José, one block north of San José State University. It is named after Our Lady of La Vang.
